Joomla relies on CASh flow..which is
C=Categorize your sections
A=Add articles
Sh=Show them on menu

Here we will make the following 
categories=
a)about
b)attractions
c)festivals
d)transport

add articles
a)about=1.Joomlaville overview 2.Joomlaville location 3.Joomlville history
b)Attractions=1.meuseum 2.zoo 3.aquarium
c)festivals=1.new years 2.independence day 3.mother's day
d)transport=1. train station 2. bus station 3. airport

sh=show them in menu

Also we upload pics via media manager 


